thread.title: Renatha Oliver

author: Renatha Oliver
title: Renatha Oliver
text: Wonderful entertainer..February 4th, he came to the Cheesecake Factory in Greensboro NC and played for my husband on his birthday. I was nervous. But he played so smooth and elegant. He made his music a piece of art. I would recommend him to anyone and I would hire him again. If you are looking for something smooth, sexy, relaxing , refreshing and entertaining all in one. Hire him, he is well worth the money.
